   <li><strong>Download</strong> 
    <ul> 
     <li><strong>Description</strong><br /> A short description displayed with the download link.</li> 
     <li><strong>File</strong><br /> File available for download on the resulting web-page. Drag an asset from the content finder or click the area to upload the file to be available for download.</li> 
    </ul> </li> 
  </ul> 
