  <h3>Layout Container</h3> 
  <note> 
   <p>Although the Layout container component is available in the classic UI, its full functionality is only available in the touch-enabled UI. For details see <a href="../../../sites/classic-ui-authoring/using/classic-page-author-responsive-layout.md">Responsive Layout</a>.</p> 
