  <h3>Tag Cloud</h3> 
  <p>A tag cloud shows a graphically presented selection of the tags applied to content within your website:</p> 
  <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/dc_tagclouduse.png" /> 
  <p>When configuring the Tag Cloud component, you can specify:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><strong>Tags to Display</strong><br /> Where the tags to be displayed are collected from. Select from a page, a page with all children or all tags.</li> 
