  <note> 
   <p>The <strong>Text</strong> component is based on the <a href="../../../sites/classic-ui-authoring/using/classic-page-author-rich-text-editor.md">Rich Text editor</a>, as is the <strong><a href="#table">Table</a></strong> component.</p> 
   <p>It is recommended to use the <strong>Table</strong> component for tables, although they can also be constructed with the <strong>Text</strong> component.</p> 
  </note> 
  <p>The Text component lets you enter a text block using a WYSIWYG editor, with functionality provided by the <a href="../../../sites/classic-ui-authoring/using/classic-page-author-rich-text-editor.md">Rich Text editor</a>. A selection of icons allow you to format your text, including font characteristics, alignment, links, lists and indentation.</p> 
  <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/dc_text.png" /> 
  <p>When you open the <strong>Styles</strong> tab of the <strong>Edit</strong> dialog you can also set:</p> 
