  <p>The formatted text will then be shown on the page; the actual design will depend on the site CSS:</p> 
  <img imageRotate="0" src="assets/dc_text_use.png" /> 
  <p>For more detailed information about the Text component and the functionality provided by the Rich Text editor, see the <a href="../../../sites/classic-ui-authoring/using/classic-page-author-rich-text-editor.md">Rich Text Editor</a> page.<br /> </p> 
